<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id746a5649-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s21704A"><num value="21704A">§ 21704A.</num><heading> Nondiscrimination</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The requirements for holding a staff position in the corporation may not discriminate on the basis of race, color, religion, sex, or national origin.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id746a564a-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/116/35/s4/a">Pub. L. 116–35, § 4(a)</ref>, <date date="2019-07-30">July 30, 2019</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/133/1046">133 Stat. 1046</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
